data.title: Alexandra of Denmark, Queen of Great Britain Wife of Edward VII
data.meta_description:
Title -  Alexandra of Denmark, Queen of Great Britain
 
Description -  Alexandra of Denmark (December 1, 1844 - November 20, 1925), Queen of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Ireland and Empress of India as the wife of King-Emperor Edward VII.
 
Description Source -  Bio from Wikipedia
 
Year -  c. 1902
